dialogStrings:
“I am the Time Guardian.
Ye who seek the knowledge of the Ancients.
I control the time, select your path.”

“What is it you wish, seeker of knowledge?”
{CHOICE}Speed up time
{CHOICE}Go back in time

“How fast would ye move time?”
{CHOICE}Just a bit
{CHOICE}A little more
{CHOICE}Plenty
{CHOICE}Cancel

{PURPLE}[MENU]{WHITE}: Leave it up to the Guard
{PURPLE}[OK]{WHITE}: Spin
{PURPLE}[CANCEL]{WHITE}: Proceed now!

{PURPLE}[MENU]{WHITE}: Move it myself
